	<h1>About</h1>
	<p class="left_align">The HartPR is a competitive ranking system and tournament archive for the game Super Smash Bros. Melee, created by <a href="https://www.twitter.com/UW_Dempsey">Michael Hartley</a> and <a href="https://www.twitter.com/dz_ssbm">Mitch Dzugan</a>. The goal of our site is to provide an objective indicator of a player's current rank in the Washington Melee community. </p>
